        COUNT(*) AS count,
        AVG(c4_number) AS avg_c4,
        c2,
        MIN(c1_number) AS min_c1,

        c2 = 'ashes are burning' OR 
        c1_number IN (1981, 1973) OR 
        c1_number = 1977
